General.Name: Zhejiang Yingfeng Technology Co Ltd
General.Description: Zhejiang Yingfeng Technology Co., Ltd. engages in the textiles printing and dyeing processing business in China. The company is involved in the printing and dyeing activities for knitted and woven fabrics. It also exports its products. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Shaoxing, China.
